ZH: 我的腰带太松了，无法系紧。
EN: My belt is too loose, I can't fasten it.

ZH: 她的腰带上有个漂亮的扣子。
EN: There is a beautiful buckle on her belt.

ZH: 他的腰带是用皮革制成的。
EN: His belt is made of leather.

ZH: 这条腰带的颜色与我的鞋子相配。
EN: The color of this belt matches my shoes.

ZH: 你能帮我打个腰带的孔吗？
EN: Can you help me punch a hole in my belt?

ZH: 她的腰带是按照她的腰围量身定制的。
EN: Her belt is custom-made according to her waist size.

ZH: 这条腰带有一个精致的刺绣花纹。
EN: This belt has a delicate embroidered pattern on it.

ZH: 我刚买了一条新的腰带。
EN: I just bought a new belt.

ZH: 老人把腰带细细地系好。
EN: The old man tightly fastened his belt.

ZH: 腰带是他的工作服的一部分。
EN: The belt is part of his uniform.

ZH: 我的腰带掉了一根线。
EN: There is a loose thread on my belt.

ZH: 这条腰带不适合我，太长了。
EN: This belt doesn't fit me, it's too long.

ZH: 她用腰带把长发束起来。
EN: She used a belt to tie up her long hair.

ZH: 这条腰带很结实，不易断裂。
EN: This belt is sturdy and not easily broken.

ZH: 他腰带上戴着一个银质的背包扣。
EN: He has a silver belt buckle on his belt.

ZH: 我的腰带松了，需要重新调整一下。
EN: My belt is loose, I need to readjust it.

ZH: 这条腰带是我亲手织的。
EN: I handwove this belt myself.

